          <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Y.</ENAMEX> pestis (representing a more
          <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">basal</ENAMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">branch</ENAMEX> of the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Enterobacteriaceae</ENAMEX>) or 
